kid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, the talented gymnast has already made her irrevocable mark on the sport as the first Black gymnast to win the all-around title in 2012, her first Olympic games in London.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 2112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2105, \"end\": 2111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999997910527091, \"rank\": 1.7386044321160047e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the talented gymnast\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"her irrevocable mark\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Black gymnast\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-around title\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2068}, {\"ngram\": \"her first Olympic games\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As her ankle heals and her training continues, Douglas is thankful that her body can recover and possibly put her back on the roster in 2028.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2161, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\", \"score\": 0.9663936580741216, \"rank\": 0.034774026926301535, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her ankle\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2126}, {\"ngram\": \"her training\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2149}, {\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"the roster\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She toldE!\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"News: \\\"I was super grateful, and still am, that I have the body type that I have, and I can still do it at the age of 28 and even at 32 in LA.\\\"\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"News\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"the body type\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since 2016, her eight-year hiatus has changed her mindset completely.\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her eight-year hiatus\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"her mindset\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the games in Rio, Douglas wasn't sure she would return to the sport, believing that she may have already aged out at 20.\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2502, \"end\": 2505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999985510650314, \"rank\": 1.448937119496639e-06, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2507, \"end\": 2514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\", \"score\": 0.9663936580741216, \"rank\": 0.034774026926301535, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I did take that six-year break, I was like, 'I can not do it.'\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that six-year break\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was always thinking about coming back to gymnastics, but I was like, I do not know, because it's always, 'You have to be 16.\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have to be fresh,'\\\" she admitted.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was called old at my second Olympic games.\\\"\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my second Olympic games\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That said, changing her mental outlook was about changing her physical routine.\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her mental outlook\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2931}, {\"ngram\": \"her physical routine\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Douglas focused on her diet, finding the right regimen that strengthened her body and kept her energized during workouts - and her workouts are not easy.\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 3126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2973, \"end\": 2980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\", \"score\": 0.9663936580741216, \"rank\": 0.034774026926301535, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her diet\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3000}, {\"ngram\": \"the right regimen\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3027}, {\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3054}, {\"ngram\": \"workouts\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3093}, {\"ngram\": \"her workouts\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Douglas confessed: \\\"When I hit the gym, it's very intense.\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3128, \"end\": 3135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\", \"score\": 0.9663936580741216, \"rank\": 0.034774026926301535, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Aircraft_Company\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will push myself to the brink.\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the brink\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I literally will do the most, like weights head-to-toe, a lot of cardio, a lot of strength training, seriously, all of it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"weights\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3262}, {\"ngram\": \"toe\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3281}, {\"ngram\": \"cardio\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3291}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3298}, {\"ngram\": \"strength training\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3396, \"end\": 3407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.606817930252042e-15, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\